  "extraHighlightWords": [],
  "sentences": [
    {
      "en": "Sunday. Flipping back through this diary, I realized I forgot to mention a whole bunch of small, random things from this year, so here they are, all at once.",
      "zh": "星期天。翻回這本日記前面，我發現今年還有一大堆零散的小事忘了寫，所以就一次全部補在這裡。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I never mentioned that our neighbor, Mrs. Huang, is a retired firewoman who still keeps her old helmet on a shelf by her front door.",
      "zh": "我從沒提過我們鄰居黃太太，她是一位退休的女消防員，到現在還把她的舊頭盔擺在門口的架子上。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I also never mentioned that a real police officer once gave our whole class a brief, friendly talk about basic street safety near school.",
      "zh": "我也沒提過，有一位真正的警官曾經在學校附近，給我們全班一場簡短又親切的基本街道安全小演講。"
    },
    {
      "en": "There was a foreigner visiting our neighborhood last spring, clearly lost, and William proudly gave him directions that were almost entirely wrong.",
      "zh": "去年春天有位外國人在我們附近迷路，William 很得意地給了他指路，結果幾乎全部指錯方向。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I forgot to mention that Sophia was once a housewife for many years before she started selling homemade snacks at the local market for extra income.",
      "zh": "我忘了提，Sophia 曾經當了很多年的家庭主婦，後來才開始在當地市場賣自製小點心，多賺一點收入。"
    },
    {
      "en": "One weekend, a street singer performed near the night market, and Bernice insisted his voice was better than anything on the radio.",
      "zh": "有個週末，一位街頭歌手在夜市附近表演，Bernice 堅持他的聲音比廣播裡任何一首歌都還好聽。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I never wrote about the time a kind old sir at the bus stop gave William his umbrella during a sudden rainstorm and refused any thanks.",
      "zh": "我從沒寫過那次，一位親切的老先生在公車站，突然下雨時把他的傘給了 William，還拒絕接受任何道謝。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I also skipped mentioning the school poet who visited our class once, reading a poem so brilliant it made even the noisiest students go completely quiet.",
      "zh": "我也漏掉提到那位來我們班訪問過一次的校園詩人，他唸的一首詩實在太出色，讓連最吵鬧的學生都安靜了下來。"
    },
    {
      "en": "There was a moment I forgot to record: William dressed up as a cowboy for a school costume day, complete with a plastic toy gun he was very proud of.",
      "zh": "有個時刻我忘了記下來：William 有一次學校變裝日打扮成牛仔，還配了一把他非常自豪的玩具塑膠槍。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I never described how beautiful the sunset looked one evening, the whole sky glowing a shade of gold that made even William stop running for a full minute.",
      "zh": "我從沒描述過某天傍晚夕陽有多美，整片天空發著一種金色的光芒，連 William 都因此停止奔跑整整一分鐘。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I forgot to mention Perry's brief, dramatic phase of being deaf to every single command except the word \"dinner,\" which he somehow always heard perfectly.",
      "zh": "我忘了提 Perry 有一段誇張的時期，對每個指令都像聾了一樣，唯獨「晚餐」這個字，他永遠都能完美聽見。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I never mentioned my brief obsession with a very strict diet plan I found online, which lasted exactly one day before I gave up and ate a whole bowl of noodles.",
      "zh": "我從沒提過我曾經短暫迷上一份在網路上找到的超嚴格飲食計畫，結果只撐了一天就放棄，吃掉了一整碗麵。"
    },
    {
      "en": "There was a day I completely forgot to write about: a sudden power outage left our whole street dark for two hours, and we ate dinner by candlelight like it was an adventure.",
      "zh": "有一天我完全忘了寫：一場突然的停電讓我們整條街暗了兩個小時，我們就著燭光吃晚餐，感覺像一場冒險。"
    },
    {
      "en": "I forgot to mention that our class has one classmate who is famously clever at math but somehow cannot spell his own last name correctly half the time.",
      "zh": "我忘了提，我們班有一位同學數學出了名的聰明，卻有一半的時間連自己的姓都拼不對。"
    },
    {
      "en": "Lesson of this catch-up entry: a whole year holds way more small moments than any diary can ever fully contain, no matter how much I try to write down.",
      "zh": "這篇補寫日記的心得：一整年裝著的小小片刻，遠比任何一本日記能完整收下的還多，不管我多努力寫下來都一樣。"
    }
  ],
